1
00:00:01,346 --> 00:00:02,873
You.

2
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:07,187
I was waiting for you.

3
00:00:07,187 --> 00:00:09,155
Ji Hyeon Ho.

4
00:00:22,340 --> 00:00:23,554
I was out of my mind!

5
00:00:23,554 --> 00:00:24,882
I was too drunk.

6
00:00:24,882 --> 00:00:28,612
How could I kiss my ex-boyfriend!

7
00:00:30,841 --> 00:00:31,812
Let me die.

8
00:00:31,812 --> 00:00:34,328
Just let me die.

9
00:00:39,073 --> 00:00:42,336
Today, we'll be meeting at the club room at Hwayang University.

10
00:00:42,336 --> 00:00:44,094
[Don't be late!]

11
00:00:44,094 --> 00:00:45,226
Oh, I forgot.

12
00:00:45,226 --> 00:00:48,990
I'll have a club activity today.

13
00:00:48,990 --> 00:00:51,730
How will I see Hyeon Ho again?

14
00:00:53,444 --> 00:00:56,098
Shall I say I'm sick?

15
00:00:57,697 --> 00:01:00,360
No. That was a mistake on the trip.

16
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:04,514
But if I don't show up, it'll become more than just a mistake.

17
00:01:04,514 --> 00:01:05,974
Alright, I'll go.

18
00:01:05,974 --> 00:01:08,990
I'll just pretend I don't remember.

19
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:19,580
[Best Mistake 3]

20
00:01:27,106 --> 00:01:30,799
Yeon Du, you like chocolate flavor, don't you?

21
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:31,553
Yes.

22
00:01:31,553 --> 00:01:35,308
This chocolate churro is the tastiest of all chocolate-flavored snacks.

23
00:01:35,308 --> 00:01:36,273
You're right.

24
00:01:36,273 --> 00:01:38,484
You need to always stack up on these.

25
00:01:38,484 --> 00:01:41,828
Last time they were all sold out.

26
00:01:42,661 --> 00:01:45,458
This is vanilla flavored. Try it.

27
00:01:45,458 --> 00:01:48,041
Chocolate churros have a rich sweetness.

28
00:01:48,041 --> 00:01:50,194
But this one is the soft type.

29
00:01:50,194 --> 00:01:51,491
It has vanilla flavor, too?

30
00:01:51,491 --> 00:01:52,770
I've never seen this before.

31
00:01:52,770 --> 00:01:53,916
No.

32
00:01:53,916 --> 00:01:56,123
It's not just vanilla flavor.

33
00:01:56,123 --> 00:01:57,191
Look here.

34
00:01:57,191 --> 00:02:01,522
All these jewel-like cookie-shaped toppings

35
00:02:01,522 --> 00:02:03,910
will crunch and pop in your mouth.

36
00:02:03,910 --> 00:02:05,957
Sounds delicious.

37
00:02:11,025 --> 00:02:13,094
It's so good.

38
00:02:14,543 --> 00:02:16,260
You try it, too.

39
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:17,757
Me?

40
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,223
President. It's already 2:00 p.m.

41
00:02:22,223 --> 00:02:24,576
We should get started.

42
00:02:24,576 --> 00:02:26,090
Huh?

43
00:02:26,090 --> 00:02:28,520
Time flies so fast.

44
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:37,049
Alright, is everyone here?

45
00:02:37,049 --> 00:02:37,904
Then today...

46
00:02:37,904 --> 00:02:41,323
President. Two people haven't shown up yet.

47
00:02:41,323 --> 00:02:43,891
Really? Who?

48
00:02:43,891 --> 00:02:45,813
Hold on.

49
00:03:02,191 --> 00:03:04,873
Member Ji Hyeon Ho and Member Jin Se Hui.

50
00:03:04,873 --> 00:03:06,999
These two aren't here yet.

51
00:03:06,999 --> 00:03:08,110
Is that so?

52
00:03:08,110 --> 00:03:11,161
I didn't get any calls from them.

53
00:03:11,161 --> 00:03:14,233
Is Hyeon Ho not coming today?

54
00:03:15,085 --> 00:03:18,797
Is Se Hui absent because of me?

55
00:03:22,801 --> 00:03:26,612
Well, I'll call them after the meeting.

56
00:03:26,612 --> 00:03:30,350
First, let's calculate the cost of the club trip.

57
00:03:33,324 --> 00:03:35,523
Sorry for being late.

58
00:03:50,082 --> 00:03:54,317
Then we'll start to calculate... We ate so much there.

59
00:03:54,317 --> 00:03:55,795
How much is all this?

60
00:03:55,795 --> 00:03:58,384
Ye Seok, did we drink all of this?

61
00:03:58,384 --> 00:04:01,113
Um... We had some left.

62
00:04:01,113 --> 00:04:03,675
But Vice President said she should finish it all so she did.

63
00:04:03,675 --> 00:04:06,453
She's a heavy drinker.

64
00:04:06,453 --> 00:04:07,730
I'm joking.

65
00:04:07,730 --> 00:04:10,760
Anyway, we had some snacks left, Vice President.

66
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:13,630
We couldn't finish them all.

67
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:16,770
President, you took them.

68
00:04:20,340 --> 00:04:25,350
I think this picture is so good.

69
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:31,340
They didn't edit these pictures much.

70
00:04:58,962 --> 00:05:02,712
This photograph of a puppy. How should we name it?

71
00:05:07,078 --> 00:05:09,346
"I was waiting for you."

72
00:05:11,052 --> 00:05:12,545
Pardon?

73
00:05:13,489 --> 00:05:16,457
How's that for a title?

74
00:05:16,457 --> 00:05:19,842
The puppy seems to be waiting for someone.

75
00:05:34,307 --> 00:05:35,913
Okay, that's all for today.

76
00:05:35,913 --> 00:05:37,331
Well done, everyone.

77
00:05:37,331 --> 00:05:39,660
- Well done.
- Thank you.

78
00:05:46,436 --> 00:05:47,817
Yeon Du, let's go to the next class toge—

79
00:05:47,817 --> 00:05:50,075
I need to talk to you.

80
00:06:06,455 --> 00:06:09,944
Where are we going? Huh?

81
00:06:12,937 --> 00:06:14,693
It was a mistake.

82
00:06:15,664 --> 00:06:16,910
What was?

83
00:06:16,910 --> 00:06:20,364
It was just a mistake.

84
00:06:22,672 --> 00:06:24,820
What was a mistake?

85
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:27,382
The kiss at the club trip...

86
00:06:28,616 --> 00:06:31,377
Um so...

87
00:06:32,451 --> 00:06:35,034
Anyway, it was all just a mistake.

88
00:06:35,034 --> 00:06:37,354
And frankly,

89
00:06:37,354 --> 00:06:41,185
I was too drunk to remember anything.

90
00:06:44,313 --> 00:06:47,538
So let's make it as if it never happened.

91
00:06:47,538 --> 00:06:49,518
Understand?

92
00:06:49,518 --> 00:06:52,076
Then... Bye.

93
00:06:52,076 --> 00:06:54,040
I refuse.

94
00:06:56,624 --> 00:06:58,209
That wasn't a mistake for me.

95
00:06:58,209 --> 00:06:59,422
And I remember everything.

96
00:06:59,422 --> 00:07:02,120
How can I just forget it all?

97
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:05,073
Well that's...

98
00:07:05,073 --> 00:07:07,351
Just forget it.

99
00:07:08,278 --> 00:07:09,691
Well...

100
00:07:10,906 --> 00:07:13,586
What? What's this?

101
00:07:13,586 --> 00:07:15,385
What?

102
00:07:20,237 --> 00:07:23,101
You started it.

103
00:07:24,918 --> 00:07:27,683
So there's no stopping.

104
00:07:27,683 --> 00:07:30,147
Wh...What!

105
00:07:43,313 --> 00:07:44,429
What is this?

106
00:07:44,429 --> 00:07:46,939
Put yourself in her shoes.

107
00:07:46,939 --> 00:07:48,141
What?

108
00:07:48,141 --> 00:07:50,181
You keep hovering around her.

109
00:07:50,181 --> 00:07:53,469
That might be very uncomfortable for her.

110
00:07:54,281 --> 00:07:57,710
You two are no longer together.

111
00:07:59,219 --> 00:08:01,855
Look who's talking.

112
00:08:01,855 --> 00:08:05,934
You bumping into Jin Se Hui, is it so uncomfortable?

113
00:08:06,895 --> 00:08:13,179
But you know, we're not like that.

114
00:08:13,179 --> 00:08:14,868
Unlike being uncomfortable around each other.

115
00:08:14,868 --> 00:08:17,974
We're not so frivolous like you.

116
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:24,012
Look at yourself, you're just her senior.

117
00:08:24,693 --> 00:08:27,799
Just a senior and nothing more.

118
00:08:28,422 --> 00:08:31,063
So mind your own business.

119
00:08:31,063 --> 00:08:34,557
About Yeon Du, I know much better than you.

120
00:08:48,418 --> 00:08:50,386
Huh?

121
00:08:50,386 --> 00:08:53,699
It's you again!

122
00:08:53,699 --> 00:08:56,512
Hey. Come here.

123
00:09:00,053 --> 00:09:02,574
Why are you here again?

124
00:09:02,574 --> 00:09:04,335
I'm in the club.

125
00:09:04,335 --> 00:09:05,961
Then just go home.

126
00:09:05,961 --> 00:09:08,134
Why are you hanging out in the hall?

127
00:09:08,134 --> 00:09:10,706
I was on my way until you called on me.

128
00:09:10,706 --> 00:09:13,312
Don't go wandering around.

129
00:09:13,312 --> 00:09:16,219
Also if you're planning something fishy,

130
00:09:16,219 --> 00:09:18,535
just forget it!

131
00:09:19,325 --> 00:09:23,602
If some kind of accident happens, you'll be the first one on the line.

132
00:09:23,602 --> 00:09:24,787
Got it?

133
00:09:24,787 --> 00:09:26,071
What accident?

134
00:09:26,071 --> 00:09:26,965
Whatever.

135
00:09:26,965 --> 00:09:29,566
An accident you're involved, or an accident you're not involved.

136
00:09:29,566 --> 00:09:31,488
I will suspect you first.

137
00:09:31,488 --> 00:09:33,187
No, suspect only you.

138
00:09:33,187 --> 00:09:36,325
No, I'll just think it's you.

139
00:09:37,695 --> 00:09:40,592
- Assistant.
- What?

140
00:09:42,303 --> 00:09:43,489
Did you lose weight?

141
00:09:43,489 --> 00:09:45,278
Weight? Do I look slim?

142
00:09:45,278 --> 00:09:47,752
Yes, you seem to have lost some.

143
00:09:47,752 --> 00:09:52,427
While you're at it, focus on shaping up and just let it go on me.

144
00:09:53,612 --> 00:09:55,157
You. Hey!

145
00:09:55,157 --> 00:09:55,977
Hey!

146
00:09:55,977 --> 00:09:58,255
That punk.

147
00:09:58,255 --> 00:10:00,972
He always takes off first.

148
00:10:02,031 --> 00:10:03,731
Hey! Hey, you!

149
00:10:03,731 --> 00:10:06,619
I've got my eyes on you! Got it?

150
00:10:06,619 --> 00:10:08,979
You're just a piece of meat.

151
00:10:12,928 --> 00:10:17,155
Right, a crush is nothing.

152
00:10:17,155 --> 00:10:21,298
I can come here whenever I miss her and just wait forever.

153
00:10:21,298 --> 00:10:23,391
This is a crush.

154
00:10:28,613 --> 00:10:30,810
Did I come too early?

155
00:10:31,445 --> 00:10:33,762
When is Seol coming?

156
00:10:40,491 --> 00:10:42,876
Seo Ju Ho?

157
00:10:42,876 --> 00:10:46,023
Was he waiting for me?

158
00:10:48,043 --> 00:10:52,650
Seol, are you on your way home?

159
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:54,713
Um, yes...

160
00:10:54,713 --> 00:10:56,524
I'm also on my way home.

161
00:10:56,524 --> 00:11:00,432
What a coincidence... it's good to see you.

162
00:11:03,785 --> 00:11:06,375
You got off early.

163
00:11:06,375 --> 00:11:08,170
I had a club meeting today.

164
00:11:08,170 --> 00:11:11,387
The TA told us to take a load of pictures.

165
00:11:11,387 --> 00:11:13,353
It was too much.

166
00:11:13,353 --> 00:11:14,985
Excuse me.

167
00:11:14,985 --> 00:11:16,809
Yes?

168
00:11:16,809 --> 00:11:20,703
Last time you told me to take advantage of you, right?

169
00:11:21,829 --> 00:11:24,544
Yes, I did.

170
00:11:25,467 --> 00:11:28,743
Then can I do that today?

171
00:11:33,009 --> 00:11:36,152
Did you enjoy your class today?

172
00:11:36,152 --> 00:11:37,797
Hey, Seol!

173
00:11:40,051 --> 00:11:42,181
Seo Ju Ho.

174
00:11:42,971 --> 00:11:44,931
You have company.

175
00:11:44,931 --> 00:11:45,821
Hello.

176
00:11:45,821 --> 00:11:49,732
This is the third time seeing you.

177
00:11:49,732 --> 00:11:52,287
Why is he counting it?

178
00:11:52,287 --> 00:11:54,284
- Pardon?
- Yes?

179
00:11:54,284 --> 00:11:56,441
Oh, yes.

180
00:11:56,441 --> 00:11:59,113
It's already the third time.

181
00:12:01,171 --> 00:12:04,434
But Ju Ho, what brings you here?

182
00:12:04,434 --> 00:12:06,651
To see you, of course.

183
00:12:06,651 --> 00:12:08,109
Did you have your meal yet?

184
00:12:08,109 --> 00:12:09,892
You haven't, right? Then let's go have a meal with me.

185
00:12:09,892 --> 00:12:12,182
Um... Well...

186
00:12:12,182 --> 00:12:15,579
I have an assignment to do today.

187
00:12:17,296 --> 00:12:19,440
With Senior Dae Yeong.

188
00:12:26,719 --> 00:12:28,359
Is that so?

189
00:12:33,851 --> 00:12:35,789
Then let me come along.

190
00:12:36,898 --> 00:12:39,262
I can wait until you're done.

191
00:12:39,262 --> 00:12:42,860
We can eat after you're done.

192
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:44,589
Let's go.

193
00:12:49,533 --> 00:12:51,309
What should I do?

194
00:12:51,309 --> 00:12:54,390
Should I just tell him the truth?

195
00:12:54,390 --> 00:12:58,678
No. It's too late for that now.

196
00:12:58,678 --> 00:13:03,639
We'll just have to do the assignment for real.

197
00:13:03,639 --> 00:13:04,816
Pardon?

198
00:13:04,816 --> 00:13:06,519
What assignment?

199
00:13:06,519 --> 00:13:09,379
Don't worry. Just follow me.

200
00:13:14,267 --> 00:13:16,166
Aren't you coming, Seol?

201
00:13:20,189 --> 00:13:22,572
Yeah, I'm coming.

202
00:13:32,299 --> 00:13:35,162
[Movie Ticket]
[Coconut Friends vs. Tyrannosaurus]

203
00:13:35,162 --> 00:13:36,685
Coconut Friends...

204
00:13:36,685 --> 00:13:38,798
Tyrannosaurus?

205
00:13:40,461 --> 00:13:43,168
- Excuse me.
- Yes?

206
00:13:43,168 --> 00:13:45,980
Didn't you say you have an assignment?

207
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:47,966
This is the assignment.

208
00:13:50,264 --> 00:13:53,032
Watching and reviewing a movie.

209
00:13:53,032 --> 00:13:54,410
I need to watch a movie

210
00:13:54,435 --> 00:13:58,066
by this week and write a review.

211
00:13:58,066 --> 00:14:01,567
Isn't that right, Seol?

212
00:14:01,567 --> 00:14:03,873
Yes, um...

213
00:14:06,782 --> 00:14:09,117
It's a weird movie.

214
00:14:22,282 --> 00:14:24,149
It's starting.

215
00:14:35,894 --> 00:14:37,294
Who do you think will win?

216
00:14:37,294 --> 00:14:40,589
I'd go for the Tyrannosaurus.

217
00:14:40,589 --> 00:14:42,329
Me too.

218
00:14:42,329 --> 00:14:43,680
- I knew it.
- Yes.

219
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:45,595
I knew it.

220
00:14:55,562 --> 00:14:56,893
Seol.

221
00:14:56,893 --> 00:14:58,992
This place does the best pasta.

222
00:14:58,992 --> 00:15:00,955
Have a bite.

223
00:15:14,142 --> 00:15:17,492
I didn't say you could join.

224
00:15:17,492 --> 00:15:20,330
Hey! That's so mean.

225
00:15:20,330 --> 00:15:22,036
We even watched a movie together.

226
00:15:22,036 --> 00:15:23,159
That was for the assignment.

227
00:15:23,159 --> 00:15:26,026
I didn't enjoy tagging along, either.

228
00:15:26,026 --> 00:15:28,878
Well it was for the assignment.

229
00:15:28,878 --> 00:15:30,948
Assignment?

230
00:15:30,948 --> 00:15:33,016
Assignment. What assignment?

231
00:15:33,016 --> 00:15:34,922
Another assignment?

232
00:15:36,258 --> 00:15:38,704
Understanding dining culture.

233
00:15:38,704 --> 00:15:40,208
Am I right, Seol?

234
00:15:40,208 --> 00:15:41,932
Huh?

235
00:15:43,853 --> 00:15:46,061
They have the best garlic bread. Have a bite.

236
00:15:46,061 --> 00:15:48,548
Oh, okay.

237
00:15:48,548 --> 00:15:51,176
Before, it was fighting with the dinosaur.

238
00:15:51,176 --> 00:15:53,372
Now it's dining culture?

239
00:15:53,372 --> 00:15:55,203
Right.

240
00:15:56,145 --> 00:15:59,059
Oh, well. Enjoy.

241
00:16:03,279 --> 00:16:04,998
It's so good.

242
00:16:04,998 --> 00:16:07,087
- Do you need a tissue?
- I'm good.

243
00:16:07,111 --> 00:16:07,958
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

244
00:16:07,958 --> 00:16:09,816
Can you hand me a tissue?

245
00:16:09,816 --> 00:16:12,331
They don't have tissues here.

246
00:16:20,037 --> 00:16:23,523
Thanks to you, I've finished all my assignments.

247
00:16:23,523 --> 00:16:25,335
With your help,

248
00:16:25,335 --> 00:16:28,757
I think I'll get A+ for sure.

249
00:16:41,151 --> 00:16:44,286
You can use me again sometime.

250
00:16:44,286 --> 00:16:46,654
I'm really okay.

251
00:16:52,703 --> 00:16:54,657
I'll be off.

252
00:16:56,658 --> 00:16:58,375
Bye.

253
00:17:10,164 --> 00:17:14,590
He's weird. Why is he hugging you all of a sudden?

254
00:17:15,181 --> 00:17:18,435
Did he say something? What did he say?

255
00:17:18,435 --> 00:17:22,167
What, it's not for you to know.

256
00:17:22,167 --> 00:17:23,939
What do you mean?

257
00:17:23,939 --> 00:17:25,642
We are...

258
00:17:35,533 --> 00:17:41,693
We are... not in a relationship.

259
00:17:49,493 --> 00:17:51,560
I see.

260
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:54,410
It wasn't for me to know.

261
00:17:58,536 --> 00:18:00,443
I'll be off.

262
00:18:18,420 --> 00:18:20,751
What am I doing?

263
00:18:20,751 --> 00:18:23,631
I shouldn't do this to either of them.

264
00:18:39,482 --> 00:18:41,395
Yeon Du!

265
00:18:42,296 --> 00:18:43,087
Oh, hi, Unnie.

266
00:18:43,087 --> 00:18:45,100
You're still here. Thank goodness.

267
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:47,733
I worried about you.

268
00:18:47,733 --> 00:18:50,249
You didn't show up at the club meeting.

269
00:18:50,249 --> 00:18:53,526
Is it because of what happened at the club trip?

270
00:18:53,526 --> 00:18:56,011
Do you feel uncomfortable around me?

271
00:18:56,011 --> 00:18:57,697
Why would I feel uncomfortable?

272
00:18:57,697 --> 00:18:59,324
It's not like that.

273
00:18:59,324 --> 00:19:00,559
Thank god.

274
00:19:00,559 --> 00:19:02,522
That's a relief.

275
00:19:02,522 --> 00:19:06,351
It's not like that, but that's why I came here.

276
00:19:06,351 --> 00:19:08,045
Pardon?

277
00:19:08,045 --> 00:19:09,549
I'm really sorry, Yeon Du.

278
00:19:09,549 --> 00:19:11,823
I got confused with the supermarket.

279
00:19:11,823 --> 00:19:13,988
That's okay. It could happen.

280
00:19:13,988 --> 00:19:16,611
You said you were sorry that day.

281
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:20,796
- Excuse me, Unnie.
- Okay.

282
00:19:20,796 --> 00:19:21,790
Hello?

283
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:24,309
Hey, Kim Yeon Du. Did you see Everytime?

284
00:19:24,309 --> 00:19:26,160
Everytime?

285
00:19:27,098 --> 00:19:29,656
Check it quickly! Quickly!

286
00:19:34,125 --> 00:19:37,677
What is all this?

287
00:19:37,677 --> 00:19:39,781
What's the matter, Yeon Du?

288
00:19:46,710 --> 00:19:49,110
Is that her?

289
00:19:56,410 --> 00:19:59,450
Oh my, wow.

290
00:20:20,779 --> 00:20:22,188
[Next episode]
Did you finish your training?

291
00:20:22,188 --> 00:20:23,989
You didn't show it to Seung Hyeon, did you?

292
00:20:23,989 --> 00:20:26,591
I think Yeon Du is not in her right mind right now.

293
00:20:26,591 --> 00:20:28,381
Someone did to Squirtle...

294
00:20:28,381 --> 00:20:30,617
There's a photo that looks like we took it during the club trip.

295
00:20:30,617 --> 00:20:32,585
Oh, you mean that photo?

296
00:20:32,585 --> 00:20:35,320
I knew this would happen. Kim Yeon Du.

297
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:36,419
Heo Jin Su?

298
00:20:36,419 --> 00:20:37,768
You guys still haven't made up yet?

299
00:20:37,768 --> 00:20:39,511
Huh?

300
00:20:46,805 --> 00:20:50,280
[Best Mistake 3]
